{"tid":1786835,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"星政府用新法逼反對黨改fb帖文","createTime":"2019-12-17T12:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T12:47:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"de938102f95c81c424cad1f64b6c3d14f89a6ca6","tid":1786835,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:26:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20191216/RDX4UT6KBB7BNCX7WZC52QXFMU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191216%2FRDX4UT6KBB7BNCX7WZC52QXFMU%2F&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0jUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=0b44011c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191216%2FRDX4UT6KBB7BNCX7WZC52QXFMU%2F&h=f97f0f73\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20191216/RDX4UT6KBB7BNCX7WZC52QXFMU/</a><br />\n<br />\n星政府用新法逼反對黨改fb帖文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191216/large/1576424883_e4f7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191216%2Flarge%2F1576424883_e4f7.gif&h=b8748246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新加坡政府指有政黨在網上發表誤導性言論。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n新加坡政府以新設立的假資訊法，首次要求敵對政黨修改網上言論，下令新加坡民主黨（SDP）更正與就業有關的兩則facebook帖文和一則網絡文章。<br />\n<br />\n有關文章指很多新加坡人被外籍員工搶去白領職位。當局在事實核查後在網上發聲明指有關說法錯誤，「SDP發放誤導資訊，只有一個目的，就是要在本地的專業人士、管理層、行政人員和科技人員之間激起恐懼和焦慮。讓事實說話對於新加坡人不被誤導十分重要」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱打擊網絡假資訊<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：逾半首投族fb收政治資訊 網紅影響大<br />\n<br />\n當局上月已兩次引用該法例，首次要求fb出更正帖文，和要求一名反對派政黨的成員更正言論。新例亦禁止發佈意圖影響公眾意見的廣告，SDP指Google本月根據新例，禁止新加坡平台上出現政治廣告。新法例被批評打壓公民自由。政府則堅稱法例是打擊網絡假資訊的必要措施。<br />\n<br />\n政府近期越趨頻繁地引用新例的同時，外界猜測不出數月後將舉行大選。SDP指主流傳媒一向靠攏政府，新例下他們更難接觸選民。不過人民行動黨（PAP）已執政多年，反對派政黨向來勢弱，如今亦難見可對執政黨構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"7f2c7c5f62032bcd0b2e9bb8ee1f31f02f6e5c88","tid":1786835,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:27:40.000Z","msg":"喺新加坡呢啲嘢都稱唔上係「新聞」啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d454f83ccd26ed5c0da5493b39ba9eca4cec523","tid":1786835,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RU8EhU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRU8EhU3.jpg&h=c3f3defe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"643ecac25d1c46c61e0715a94edcfc32ac4606da","tid":1786835,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:32:40.000Z","msg":"人民行動黨連修憲既票數都有，鐘意點立法都得，立條法迫你改黨名都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13dfe335b5755960ca83a16805b6869d4ba37b6","tid":1786835,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:47:03.000Z","msg":"應該鼓勵新加坡每年輸入5萬個低技術單證程移民，<br />\n已獲取中国人口紅利"}]}